      "text": "Yon fwa sou yon tan, ta p' viv yon nonm yo te rele Joèl nan yon bouk ki te rele Aya."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f4c88d493-a3e0-437a-8ee5-7599be7a2b3c%2fYon+nonm+neglijan%2fA_careless_man_Page_03_Image_0001.png",
      "text": "Li pa t' gen lide pou l' estoke manje pou l' itilize a lavni, men selman gaspiye yo."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f4c88d493-a3e0-437a-8ee5-7599be7a2b3c%2fYon+nonm+neglijan%2fASP_80_a_careless_man_Page_04_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Pa gen anyen rete nan galata a."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f4c88d493-a3e0-437a-8ee5-7599be7a2b3c%2fYon+nonm+neglijan%2fASP_80_a_careless_man_Page_05_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Plant mayi yo fennen jiskaske yo chèch."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f4c88d493-a3e0-437a-8ee5-7599be7a2b3c%2fYon+nonm+neglijan%2fASP_80_a_careless_man_Page_06_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Yon van fò kònen sou tèt galata a."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f4c88d493-a3e0-437a-8ee5-7599be7a2b3c%2fYon+nonm+neglijan%2fASP_80_a_careless_man_Page_07_Image_0001.png",
      "text": "Timoun yo te goumen pou ti manje ki rete nan mamit la."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f4c88d493-a3e0-437a-8ee5-7599be7a2b3c%2fYon+nonm+neglijan%2fASP_80_a_careless_man_Page_08_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Manman te mete plat la sou tab la, e li t'ap rele byen fò sou sa pou l' bay timoun yo pwochen fwa."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/glauredarwindy%40gmail.com%2f4c88d493-a3e0-437a-8ee5-7599be7a2b3c%2fYon+nonm+neglijan%2fASP_80_a_careless_man_Page_09_Image_0001.jpg",
      "text": "Papa chita anba galri a la ap panse sou lavni."
    }
